	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Nintendulator screenshot below depicts part of the intro to Metal Slader Glory.7z &lt;Metal Slader Glory (J).nes&gt;.  <br /><br /><img src="http://i.imgur.com/19jczUj.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />The box containing the person has a horizontal, blue line at the bottom.  The blue line also appears in Nestopia.  But, it is absent in FCEUX, puNES and Mesen.  <br /><br />Does anyone have a recording of the intro from actual Famicom hardware?  The MMC5 IRQ scanline counting is off in some emulators.

		

		</td>
